  <!-- EN: [joiner_nameDef] has admitted what [joiner_pronoun] was fleeing from.\n    \n[joiner_pronoun] was supposed to marry the child of [enemyFaction_leader_nameFull], leader of [enemyFaction_name]. [joiner_pronoun] became drunk before the ceremony and vomited on the altar - a flagrant insult towards [enemyFaction_leader_nameDef]'s whole family.\n    \n[enemyFaction_leader_nameDef] swore to seek revenge on [joiner_nameDef] and all those associated with [joiner_objective], and sent [enemyFaction_pawnsPlural] to carry out the task.\n    \n{BASETEXT} -->
  <ThreatReward_MysteryThreat_Joiner.root.nodes.Delay.node.nodes.RandomNode.nodes.Sequence-0.nodes.Set-1.value.slateRef> [joiner_nameDef]已經向我們承認[joiner_pronoun]是逃出來的。\n    \n[joiner_pronoun]本來應該和[enemyFaction_name]首領[enemyFaction_leader_nameFull]的孩子結婚。[joiner_pronoun]在婚禮開始前醉酒並且嘔吐在了儀式祭壇上，這一行為被認為是[enemyFaction_leader_nameDef]整個家族的奇恥大辱。\n    \n[enemyFaction_leader_nameDef]發誓將要報複[joiner_nameDef]和所有與[joiner_objective]有關的人，並且已經派出[enemyFaction_pawnsPlural]來執行這項任務。\n    \n{BASETEXT}</ThreatReward_MysteryThreat_Joiner.root.nodes.Delay.node.nodes.RandomNode.nodes.Sequence-0.nodes.Set-1.value.slateRef>
  <!-- EN: {BASELABEL}: Chasing [joiner_nameDef] -->
